headline: 3 Reasons CPRT Has Explosive Upside Potential
summary: Over the past six months, Copart’s shares (currently trading at $47.88) have posted a disappointing 17.8% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 1.1% gain. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
